
"I promise you, I will find you and we will be happy." Harry says running in the other direction as me.
"You can't leave me!" I screamed. "Not again."
His face dropped as he turned around then continued walking. "Harry!" I cried.
This isn't possible. He can't be leaving me, he was going to get caught and once he got caught they would be after me too. There was only one way to stop this. "F-fine. I'll do it."
He stopped in his place and turned around, running up to me immediately wrapping me in a hug then wiping my tears away. He kissed my forehead then leaned in my ear whispering, "Good girl."